PrecisAppointment of RODERICK BELL as Ambassador of Canada to the Hashemite Kingdom of Jordan; KEITH CHRISTIE as Ambassador of Canada to the United Mexican States; MacKENZIE CLUGSTON as Consul General of Canada at Osaka, Japan; ALAIN DUDOIT as Ambassador of Canada to the Kingdom of Spain; PAUL DURAND as Ambassador of Canada to the Republic of Chile; RAPHAËL GIRARD as Ambassador of Canada to Romania with concurrent accreditation to the Republic of Bulgaria; PAUL HEINBECKER as Ambassador and Permanent Representative of Canada to the United Nations in New York; JEAN-PIERRE JUNEAU as Ambassador of Canada to the Federative Republic of Brazil; MICHAEL KERGIN as Ambassador of Canada to the United States of America; JEREMY K.B. KINSMAN as High Commissioner for Canada in the United Kingdom of Great Britain and Northern Ireland; WILFRID LICARI as Ambassador of Canada to the Holy See; JUDITH ST. GEORGE as Consul General of Canada at Ho Chi Minh City, Socialist Republic of Vietnam; and DOREEN STEIDLE as High Commissioner for Canada in the Republic of Singapore.
